5 K. Credits received pursuant to the Oklahoma Parental Choice
6 Tax Credit Act shall not constitute taxable income to a taxpayer who
7 received the credit on behalf of an eligible student.
8 L. No later than June 15 of each year, each participating
9 private school shall electronically provide information to confirm
10 student enrollment and tuition information for the fall and spring
